{"word":"Defilement","slug":"defilement","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Defilement</b> Laws relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=21'>Lev 7:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=43'>Lev 11:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=7'>Lev 22:7</a><br/> Caused by:<br/> - Leprosy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=3'>Lev 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=46'>Lev 13:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14'>Lev 14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=7'>Lev 22:7</a> <br/> - Gonorrhea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=15'>Lev 15:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=4'>Lev 22:4</a> <br/> - Copulation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=17'>Lev 15:17</a> <br/> - Spermatorrhea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=17'>Lev 15:17</a> <br/> - Childbirth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=12&verse=8'>Lev 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=22'>Luk 2:22</a> <br/> - Menses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=33'>Lev 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=4'>2Sa 11:4</a> <br/> - Touching the dead<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=22'>Num 19:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=20'>Num 31:20</a> <br/> - Touching carcass of any unclean animal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=40'>Lev 11:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=16'>Lev 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=8'>Lev 22:8</a> <br/> - Touching carcass of an unclean thing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=13'>Lev 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=8'>Lev 11:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=28'>Lev 11:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=38'>Lev 11:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=14&verse=57'>Lev 14:57</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=11'>Lev 15:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=11'>Deu 23:11</a> <br/> - Slaying in battle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=20'>Num 31:20</a> <br/> - Contact with sinners falsely supposed to cause<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=28'>Joh 18:28</a> <br/> Of priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=26'>Lev 16:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=28'>Lev 16:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=10'>Num 19:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=44&verse=26'>Eze 44:26</a><br/> Egyptian usage, concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=32'>Gen 43:32</a><br/><a href='S:Ablution'>Ablution</a>; <a href='S:Purification'>Purification</a>; <a href='S:Uncleanness'>Uncleanness</a>"}]}